response.overview: A town half secluded in the woods with a classic Greaser vs Soc rivalry that turns deadly after Natalie Lloyd mysteriously disappears. Her boyfriend, a Soc, and her older brother, a Greaser, blame each other for what happened but lurking in the shadows is a dark figure watching them. A dramatic adventure of these boys trying to find their ways by getting into fights, stealing cars, championship football games, and complicated relationships. All the while not knowing of the Evil that hides in the shadows.
response.title: What We Don't See
